Lewis Hamilton is getting inside teammate Nico Rosberg 's head as the German bids to win his first World Championship title , according to Rosberg .
Rosberg accused Mercedes team-mate Hamilton of deliberately compromising his race at last weekend 's Chinese Grand Prix by slowing down .
Mika Hakkinen said the British driver 's tactics saw him win a third consecutive Grand Prix ahead of the German .
Hamilton has out-qualified and out-raced Rosberg in China .